version: 0.1.0
language: typescript

=== Intent ===
purpose: Full entry view page. Shows complete entry content, media attachments, edit/delete actions, and for Daily Combined Entries shows source entries and a Re-Generate button.
source:
  kind: prd
  reference: "PRD Section 10.1 â€” Entry Detail View"
